{"tid":2421304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★股災ready！破紀錄200億淨流出　大媽狂沽騰訊美團港交所","createTime":"2021-02-24T11:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T12:08:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32f954e334ec461faedee4f2cf224bd68fbea5a9","tid":2421304,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:59:26.000Z","msg":"今日南向港股通錄得1,002億成交，再創紀錄新高，佔大市成交28.41%。其中，買入成交額錄得401.6億元；賣出成交額錄得601.2億元；全日淨流出近200億元，屬2021年第一個交易日錄得淨流走，更是2020年12月18日以來首次淨賣出，亦創港股通開通以來最大淨流入規模。<br />\n<br />\n據聯交所資料顯示，騰訊（0700）錄得49.16億元淨流出；港交所（0388）淨流走40.4億元；美團（3690）淨流出41.95億元；小米（1810）淨流走18.1億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/591466/%E5%8C%97%E6%B0%B4%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E8%BD%89%E5%90%91-%E7%A0%B4%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84200%E5%84%84%E6%B7%A8%E6%B5%81%E5%87%BA-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E7%8B%82%E6%B2%BD%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%98%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F591466%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%2590%2591-%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584200%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%25B7%25A8%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%2587%25BA-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E7%258B%2582%25E6%25B2%25BD%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%25A8%258A%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%2598%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2589%2580&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8JugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=95f41f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/591466/%E5%8C%97%E6%B0%B4%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E8%BD%89%E5%90%91-%E7%A0%B4%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84200%E5%84%84%E6%B7%A8%E6%B5%81%E5%87%BA-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E7%8B%82%E6%B2%BD%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%98%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80</a>"},{"pid":"9cf040eb3f4cae3ce42ee7416a6f14c2cd89a44a","tid":2421304,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"